{{Quote|It's knocking us down like maze-flies!!|a Cloud-rider|<ref name="Star Wars (1977) 10">[[Star Wars (1977) 10|''Star Wars'' (1977) 10]]</ref>}}
'''Maze-flies''' were slow-moving [[Insect/Legends|insects]] native to [[Aduba-3/Legends|Aduba-3]] that were easily swatted out of the air. They gave rise to the expression "to knock down like maze-flies," which was used by the local [[Cloud-Riders/Legends|Cloud-Riders]].

